                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The United Nations General Assembly held its second meeting of the day from 3 to
                    6:30 p. m. on October 6; for the record, see U.N. document A/PV.293. No voting
                    took place, as the discussion on the draft resolutions continued.</p>
            </div>
